{
  "$schema": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ScoopInstaller/Scoop/master/schema.json",
  "version": "{{VERSION}}",
  "description": "Recomendaciones Letterboxd + streaming BitTorrent con player embebido (GUI + CLI, mismo binario).",
  "homepage": "https://github.com/{{REPO}}",
  "license": "MIT",
  "url": "https://github.com/{{REPO}}/releases/download/{{TAG}}/videodrome-{{TAG}}-windows-x86_64.zip",
  "hash": "{{SHA_WIN}}",
  "bin": [
    ["videodrome.exe", "videodrome"]
  ],
  "shortcuts": [
    ["videodrome.exe", "Videodrome"]
  ],
  "depends": ["main/ffmpeg"],
  "notes": [
    "Videodrome se ha instalado con GUI + CLI en el mismo binario.",
    "  · Doble click en Start Menu (o busca 'Videodrome') → GUI.",
    "  · `videodrome recommend` en PowerShell/cmd → CLI.",
    "  · `videodrome tui` → TUI en terminal.",
    "ffmpeg (bucket 'main') se instaló como dependencia — lo usa el player embebido para transmux.",
    "Reproductor: por defecto embebido. Si prefieres VLC externo, instálalo aparte con `scoop bucket add extras && scoop install extras/vlc` y cambíalo en Ajustes."
  ],
  "checkver": {
    "github": "https://github.com/{{REPO}}"
  },
  "autoupdate": {
    "url": "https://github.com/{{REPO}}/releases/download/v$version/videodrome-v$version-windows-x86_64.zip"
  }
}
